name: Electsys-safari
tagline: Electsys++ SJTU electsys optimizer in safari
body:
# Electsys in safari

上海交通大学选课插件

Electsys是laohyx学长写的一个chrome插件，开源在Github上，项目链接为[electsys](https://github.com/laohyx/electsys)，本项目是在chrome插件的基础上移植而来。

安装请下载[electsys.safariextz](./electsys.safariextz)拖到safari中即可。
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
